  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422360/extras/1156663fd3685725c204993e602a5203.poster.avif?t=1705353428\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422360/extras/1156663fd3685725c204993e602a5203.webm?t=1705353428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422360/extras/1156663fd3685725c204993e602a5203.mp4?t=1705353428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422360/extras/41e94b2146d0abf27808370c84f62b25.avif?t=1705353428\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Summary</h2><br>The Four Paths is a strategy game where each campaign is unique because in each adventure you'll discover new stories, abilities, relics and opponents.<br>Overcome each challenge and discover all the endings that The Four Paths offers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422360/extras/cf002172a9346df3b5ebdf6ecfccbf5d.avif?t=1705353428\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strategic Battles</h2><br>Read your opponents' feelings, spend your mana strategically, follow your feelings, choose the best skills in each situation and claim victory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422360/extras/ecfea063b64da9dbbd8881dcc7eda4aa.avif?t=1705353428\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><i>More than 50 skills.<br><br>More than 10 finals.<br><br>More than 20 relics.<br><br>A nice story.<br><br>Some books.<br><br>Minigames.</i><br><br><br>",
